Package: CODECtools
Title: Support CODEC data infrastructure
Version: 0.3.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Cole", "Brokamp", , "cole.brokamp@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-0289-3151"))
Description: CODECtools provides tools for working with metadata in R and storing it alongside data in a YAML file. This package serves as the definition of the CODEC data specifications and provides helpers to contribute and validate CODEC data.
